name: Lonely Autumn - 秋
description: "That day she didn't want to serve anyone, she ran free on a lonely autumn day." Handmade painting in the fall of 2020, inspired by japanese ukiyo-e prints. Acrylic paint and gouache on japanese paper come to life with digital animation! Made by Helena Cinirla; TT- @cinirla / ig - @helenacinirla
